-// For a normalized diyfp w = f * 2^e, this function returns a (normalized)
-// cached power-of-ten c = f_c * 2^e_c, such that the exponent of the product
-// w * c satisfies (Definition 3.2 from [1])
-//
-//      alpha <= e_c + e + q <= gamma.
